Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.20,0:56:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you go back into the lifetime and it reruns.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.67,0:56:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like what's happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.35,0:56:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't like a movie where you witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.35,0:56:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,nor is it like a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.06,0:56:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reactivate that lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.09,0:56:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's simple ways of doing it, simple self-hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.29,0:56:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell anybody how to reactivate a past lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.88,0:56:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's extremely simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.70,0:56:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With profound relaxation done,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.06,0:56:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.52,0:56:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you say, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.72,0:56:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get along with horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.18,0:56:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.30,0:56:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had any problem with horses in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.10,0:56:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Never abused them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.29,0:57:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet horses have practically done me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.31,0:57:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thrown,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.49,0:57:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,stomped,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.67,0:57:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,raked up the back of the horse
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.01,0:57:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and on a bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.07,0:57:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,knocked out and unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.38,0:57:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what's with me and horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.68,0:57:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in questioning that, I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.62,0:57:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go into a profound state of relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.46,0:57:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when you go into self-hypnosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.20,0:57:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to be very, very profound,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.10,0:57:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,relaxed, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.51,0:57:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think you're completely and totally relaxed,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.73,0:57:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you aren't yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.67,0:57:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's more profound than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.69,0:57:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a profound relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.67,0:57:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In that state, the question is, I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.10,0:57:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use any device.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.42,0:57:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say, I will walk up this hill and over the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.38,0:57:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.24,0:57:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you re-experience, re-experience the life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.08,0:57:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember the life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.40,0:57:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't edit it because it's running like a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.86,0:57:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't edit it with the movie's playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.55,0:57:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that life is recalled.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.53,0:57:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And the explanation of what you're hung up on
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.53,0:57:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime now becomes quite clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.19,0:58:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a useful technique
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.35,0:58:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if you get up against a difficult block.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.69,0:58:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often, intuitively,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.25,0:58:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you know that something must have accounted for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.35,0:58:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If everybody's cheating you all your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.39,0:58:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.95,0:58:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be sure that in some lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.79,0:58:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you were cheating the hell out of everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.15,0:58:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to forgive the one in you who didn't know any better
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.79,0:58:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and place their survival on dishonesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.05,0:58:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you try to make amends for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.17,0:58:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to, anyway, you take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.76,0:58:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So one of the things about spiritual evolution is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.84,0:58:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,always to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.48,0:58:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Never assume it's caused by something out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.14,0:58:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,even more backwards in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.58,0:58:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest value of Est for those that,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.66,0:58:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that you did Est,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.66,0:58:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was that it wouldn't allow you to get away
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.90,0:58:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with any alibi or excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.66,0:58:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had to take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.90,0:58:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for whatever it was, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.28,0:59:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If your shoelace broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.05,0:59:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.69,0:59:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to take responsibility for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.46,0:59:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the human ego hates to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.04,0:59:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Takes responsibility that you're not,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.04,0:59:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,not that you're the cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.44,0:59:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're the source of it and you're activating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.62,0:59:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving energy to that belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.12,0:59:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.31,0:59:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to complete before the first break.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.90,0:59:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.90,0:59:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.02,0:59:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.02,0:59:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.02,0:59:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.02,0:59:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.02,0:59:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to complete all the academic,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.02,0:59:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,all the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.02,0:59:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All this has been covered in books and charts and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.90,0:59:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.26,0:59:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.26,0:59:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it recontextualizes the way you see yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.14,0:59:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way you see spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.24,0:59:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way you envision the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.90,0:59:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your perceptions of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.38,0:59:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of good and bad, good and evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.56,0:59:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,good and evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.56,1:00:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you really get hung up on good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.16,1:00:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.16,1:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,instead, all you can see is that people innocently
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.00,1:00:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are blindly following what they believe to be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.16,1:00:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're blindly following the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.64,1:00:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the highest good is to steal a pie from the bakery
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.90,1:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because you haven't got any money.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.44,1:00:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.10,1:00:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest good, that's the best you could do.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.78,1:00:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.78,1:00:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go hungry or you steal a pie.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.78,1:00:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say honesty isn't even possible
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.62,1:00:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,until you reach a certain level of self-sufficiency, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.84,1:00:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.84,1:00:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there could be a good time you could sacrifice yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.29,1:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for God and starve to death,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.03,1:00:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,which I don't know would make God very happy,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.73,1:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but it makes a lot of martyrs feel happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.29,1:00:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.78,1:00:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So the brain, as you see at the top,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.62,1:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've done this before,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.22,1:00:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain up to consciousness level 200
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.52,1:00:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,operates in a different way
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.92,1:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,than the brain from consciousness level 200 and over,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.32,1:01:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which is another reason to forgive people
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.92,1:01:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because below 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.22,1:01:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the way the person's brain works.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.32,1:01:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the input, the perception,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.42,1:01:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,goes through the thalamus, the emotional relay,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.82,1:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,very rapidly to the emotional center,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.32,1:01:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and the whole thing is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.62,1:01:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that process, they release adrenaline,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.22,1:01:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,fight or flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.82,1:01:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is an animal response.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.72,1:01:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This part of the brain is what dominates 85% of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.12,1:01:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty-five percent of mankind is dominated by the animal,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.64,1:01:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by the animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.53,1:01:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannot tell truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.33,1:01:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannot tell a savior from a narcissistic megalomaniac dictator
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.13,1:01:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,who's going to blow you all to kingdom come.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.72,1:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the crowds over the generations saluting people.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.92,1:01:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're calibrated at 80.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.12,1:01:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrated at 80.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.12,1:01:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.53,1:02:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the same time, we see society ridiculing
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.03,1:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that which calibrates to the thousand divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.03,1:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.63,1:02:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not mention these things in public.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.83,1:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be on the side of pedophilia,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.78,1:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not okay to mention God or have a Christmas tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.88,1:02:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called the Lucifer conversion,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.68,1:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the inability to believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.08,1:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The inability to tell the truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.08,1:02:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In which the good becomes the bad,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.48,1:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and the bad becomes the good, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.81,1:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that happens in this kind of a brain, all right,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.31,1:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because divinity threatens the narcissistic core of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.01,1:02:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,which presumes itself to be the source of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.51,1:02:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You spend your whole spiritual life trying to transcend
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.61,1:02:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the narcissist ego and its payoffs, its belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.16,1:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you finally transcend all the levels,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.50,1:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what the core of the ego is.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.80,1:03:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it got hit by the very core of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.32,1:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.92,1:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.62,1:03:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no others.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.82,1:03:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All these spiritual things talking about others,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.72,1:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,visions and others talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.38,1:03:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As you go there, there's no one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.08,1:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.68,1:03:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no others coaching you along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.68,1:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hear visions, angelic teachers.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.39,1:03:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind becomes silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.76,1:03:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left except life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.76,1:03:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.80,1:03:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only God.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.18,1:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing left when you get to the last doorway.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.66,1:03:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.79,1:03:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left that you're clinging to.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.92,1:03:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're clinging to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.27,1:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're facing the very core of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.27,1:03:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Few people know the core of the ego because they've never faced it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.27,1:03:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're facing it, you're facing the certainty
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.27,1:04:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you surrender this, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.65,1:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never faced it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.65,1:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.75,1:04:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never faced it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.75,1:04:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical death is a joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.75,1:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whooping you out of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.75,1:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And there it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.75,1:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.75,1:04:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb looking thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.84,1:04:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So stupid looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.84,1:04:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody know this?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.84,1:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Been out of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.84,1:04:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here been out of the body?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.97,1:04:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.97,1:04:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how dumb the body looks.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.97,1:04:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It lays there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.97,1:04:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.97,1:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you're really up against the nitty-gritty now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.57,1:04:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because realize the last thing that you haven't surrendered to God is your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.57,1:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've surrendered your life pattern, your life habits, your life beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.82,1:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But not life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.82,1:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then comes an absolute terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.98,1:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As you surrender life, the knowingness, which I'm repeating now, which was known at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.84,1:04:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it, is a vibration and a frequency in the aura because your mind is silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.84,1:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk straight ahead no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.58,1:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.77,1:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe to let go of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.77,1:05:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can tell you that with a frequency and a vibration who hasn't done it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.34,1:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So with absolute terror, and for a few moments you die, and it is an agony of death.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.34,1:05:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You agonizingly die.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.76,1:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.23,1:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite splendor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.39,1:05:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite splendor of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.48,1:05:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mind is struck silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.48,1:05:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is struck silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.87,1:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what the ego dreaded all this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.12,1:05:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the ego dreaded all this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.12,1:05:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it hates any mention of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.16,1:05:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is the source of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.19,1:05:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.19,1:05:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so firmly convinced that the ego is your source of life,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.19,1:05:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd rather go through all kinds of tortures, endless lifetimes of hell, agony,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.19,1:05:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.99,1:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego has you convinced.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.05,1:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.05,1:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because since the beginning of life, the first bacteria, that was true.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.05,1:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.05,1:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Except that you're not an amoeba.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.66,1:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.66,1:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny as a human being is to transcend identification
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.66,1:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and limitation of the linear animal world.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.66,1:06:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you go over 200 now, the brain physiology changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.88,1:06:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The prefrontal cortex now begins to play a greater part.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.96,1:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course the most important thing that happens at 200
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.96,1:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the emergence of the kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.96,1:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the kundalini energy, which we've spoken of before,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.96,1:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very unique spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.96,1:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At 200 and up now, the spiritual energy shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.12,1:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It runs up through, classically described as running up through the chakra system.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.22,1:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's a radiance from within.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.22,1:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And this radiance transforms perception and understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.25,1:07:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and how you see and experience the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.25,1:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we've mentioned, in the high 500s,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.25,1:07:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it brings on the so-called siddhis,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.25,1:07:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,which are sort of paranormal phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.25,1:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the miraculous, capacity for the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.25,1:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So this now, the most important thing about this
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.25,1:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you develop an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.96,1:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Under 200, you don't have an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.50,1:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200, you have an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.50,1:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Under 200, there is group karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.50,1:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Above 200, there's individual karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.98,1:07:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rather profound statement.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.52,1:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask that for this group.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.52,1:07:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That statement is a fact, Lord, and resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.52,1:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Add a level of confidence of 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.52,1:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute level of confidence, then, it says.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.39,1:07:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so. That is so.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.55,1:08:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It explains mass phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.55,1:08:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people will come in, then, as a group,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.12,1:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,not as an individual.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.12,1:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You see a mass of birds like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.12,1:08:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,they share an individual unit.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.12,1:08:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One, they share the same karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.12,1:08:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not seeing 10,000 different bird karmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.12,1:08:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They share a oneness.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.12,1:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The oneness of the group dominates.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.25,1:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200 now, you have a unique personal karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.44,1:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200, one of that bird is going to be different
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.44,1:08:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,than the rest of the birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.44,1:08:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's destined now to go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.64,1:08:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.49,1:08:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a level of consciousness and social problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.49,1:08:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We say,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.49,1:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to integrity is to stop blaming anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.48,1:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not blaming anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.03,1:08:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just start from where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.09,1:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't necessary to blame.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.09,1:09:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just see how that feeds the ego and weakens you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.09,1:09:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if somebody is to blame?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.21,1:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.98,1:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.98,1:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.98,1:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your thumb, you lost it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.24,1:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.62,1:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.69,1:09:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it have a karmic precedent?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.72,1:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure did.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.72,1:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure did.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.20,1:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure did.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.20,1:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing just happens by accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.26,1:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.26,1:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So we take, then, responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.26,1:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the level of consciousness moves up,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.26,1:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that happiness is not related to out-there-ness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.26,1:09:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's related to level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.26,1:09:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the happiness rate is concordant
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.26,1:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,with level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.26,1:09:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Up here, you don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.87,1:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have an apple and a cock to sleep on
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.87,1:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and be completely happy and delighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.87,1:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At a lower level, you can have millions and commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.44,1:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.80,1:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to finish all the academic,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.76,1:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for those who haven't been here before.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.76,1:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.88,1:10:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.81,1:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this is the same thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.83,1:10:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed somewhat differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.83,1:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you see is below the level of 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.83,1:10:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,this line should really be,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.83,1:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed here,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.83,1:10:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,below the level of 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.83,1:10:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you see how the rate of happiness drops off.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.83,1:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So although there's temporary gain,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.83,1:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the pleasure in hating people,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.83,1:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,pleasure in feeling sorry for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.83,1:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,pleasure in getting even,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.83,1:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,pleasure in blowing up a busload of children,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.83,1:10:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not actual happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.83,1:10:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only once you cross over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.83,1:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You see automatically it jumps,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.83,1:10:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,just at 200, then at 250.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.83,1:10:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As you go up,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.83,1:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the rate of happiness finally reaches 100%.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.83,1:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally reach a condition
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.24,1:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in which your inner state
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.24,1:11:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is completely immune to the external world.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.24,1:11:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They say,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.76,1:11:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they say,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.76,1:11:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to be shot tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.76,1:11:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, all right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.76,1:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.95,1:11:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you experience that stage,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.95,1:11:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.11,1:11:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the inner is so complete
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.11,1:11:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that what happens in the inner
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.24,1:11:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the outer is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.33,1:11:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.33,1:11:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a convenience.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.33,1:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you die in the snow,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.33,1:11:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you die in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.33,1:11:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.56,1:11:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I remember climbing in a big bank of snow,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.56,1:11:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told this story many times,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.56,1:11:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.56,1:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And just to get out of the wind
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.56,1:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the blizzard,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.56,1:11:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it was pitch black,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.56,1:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,10 below zero in the blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.65,1:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I reached, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.65,1:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I dug out in the hole in the snow,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.65,1:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it was all crusty,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.65,1:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,this big pile of snow,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.65,1:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,dug a little cave
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.65,1:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and went in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.07,1:12:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.61,1:12:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,oh God, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.61,1:12:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was being dissolved
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.48,1:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,into an infinite presence of love
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.48,1:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.48,1:12:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It dissolved all sense of personal self.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.48,1:12:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It dissolved time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.83,1:12:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It dissolved physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.83,1:12:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It dissolved anticipation.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.65,1:12:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the body survived or breathed or not
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.65,1:12:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,was totally irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.65,1:12:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not even interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.45,1:12:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,People say,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.45,1:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,gee, what if I keep doing spiritual work?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.52,1:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I might die or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.52,1:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, when that comes,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.52,1:12:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't care whether you die or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.52,1:12:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.52,1:12:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.52,1:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The personal self dies
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.52,1:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's excess baggage.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.52,1:12:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you sit down in excess baggage.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.52,1:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we do all the slides?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.96,1:12:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She keeps them secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.96,1:13:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.04,1:13:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we did the rate of happiness, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.06,1:13:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to move along
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.06,1:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because by the break we're going to have that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.06,1:13:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.06,1:13:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.88,1:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.88,1:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can slow down.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.88,1:13:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we can move faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.74,1:13:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.74,1:13:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.74,1:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's where we ended last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.84,1:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're beginning there,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.84,1:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,those of you who are linear
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.84,1:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and able to follow things
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.84,1:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,from one thing to the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.06,1:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, before that we had
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.06,1:13:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,31 characteristics of spiritual integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.01,1:13:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we do have it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.56,1:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.20,1:13:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to finish that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.90,1:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to finish that by what time?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.90,1:13:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.90,1:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.90,1:13:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.90,1:13:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.90,1:13:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only 31 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.90,1:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We can cover that in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.90,1:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we've distilled, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.19,1:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with consciousness research then,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.19,1:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you can distill the degree of integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.19,1:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,purity, level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.19,1:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of anything or anyone anywhere in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.38,1:14:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just through intuitive knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.38,1:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody with any kind of spiritual intuitive knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.38,1:14:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,would be able to come up with the same chart.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.38,1:14:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to, without naming specifics,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.64,1:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to differentiate
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.64,1:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous teachers and organizations
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.64,1:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from those which deviate
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.64,1:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from the straight and narrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.64,1:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When people read my books,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.82,1:14:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing, trouble they have
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.82,1:14:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is they've got to get past
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.82,1:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria and Excelsior's deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.08,1:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the second tripper I put in there,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.08,1:14:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the second mind is called
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.08,1:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,straight and narrow is the path.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.08,1:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is straight and narrow is the path,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.08,1:14:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, because that which is complete
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.27,1:14:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and total within itself has no needs,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.27,1:14:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,has no needs.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.27,1:14:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can tell the spiritual integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.27,1:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,from lack of integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.27,1:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,by the degree of neediness
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.27,1:15:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that it presents to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.27,1:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Proselytizing, trying to get you to sign up,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.40,1:15:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,take oaths, swear on things.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.00,1:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is non-integrous is seeking gain,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.92,1:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is looking for gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.92,1:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants to influence you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.92,1:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants to enroll you,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.92,1:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,dominate you, control you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.92,1:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we don't invite anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.37,1:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to follow our work.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.37,1:15:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not invite anyone here,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.66,1:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,nor do I even recommend
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.66,1:15:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that you follow this work at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.66,1:15:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're either dragged to it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.94,1:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.20,1:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But we certainly don't try to
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.20,1:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,sell anybody on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.20,1:15:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.71,1:15:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,selling, enthusing, signing up,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.90,1:16:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,multi-level marketing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.28,1:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want anybody to take any oaths.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.28,1:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an oath.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.89,1:16:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.50,1:16:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Previous lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.50,1:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,one lecture got together.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.50,1:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All took the same oath
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.66,1:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,about 300 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.66,1:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's another author.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.66,1:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two authors here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.20,1:16:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We had four authors here
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.20,1:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,one time in Canada.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.20,1:16:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We say take no oaths.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.20,1:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.20,1:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.20,1:16:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,what the long-term consequence is.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.20,1:16:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, if I ever so-and-so,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.36,1:16:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,may the reverse be my lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.36,1:16:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.36,1:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually it's if you leave them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.40,1:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.40,1:16:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get a rattlesnake
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.49,1:16:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in your mailbox or
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.49,1:16:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,some horrible thing will befall you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.49,1:16:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you make an oath,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.49,1:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you're bound by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.49,1:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bound by out-there-ness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.49,1:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just bound yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.49,1:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, three, four lifetimes later
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.20,1:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is payback time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.20,1:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.74,1:17:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God I only promised one thumb.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.35,1:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could have been worse things
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.67,1:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you could have promised, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.67,1:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.72,1:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I write this oath,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.67,1:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,may I lose 50% of my assets.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.28,1:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.63,1:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you sold out your freedom.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.63,1:17:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Never allow any people
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.63,1:17:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to rule over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.63,1:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There are not rulers in this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.24,1:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There are not rulers.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.36,1:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That misinterpretation comes out of the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.65,1:17:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,downside of the classic Indian guruism.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.65,1:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The worship of the guru.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.65,1:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Western person doesn't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.78,1:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the worship of the guru.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.78,1:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.84,1:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the exploitation of the Indian guru
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.84,1:18:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,took place in the course
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.84,1:18:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the last couple of decades.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.84,1:18:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over the internet.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.84,1:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The exploitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.84,1:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a teacher doesn't want any power over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.42,1:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't want any power at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.42,1:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.42,1:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who needs power
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.42,1:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when you have all the power that is?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.84,1:18:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember in a very high state
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.84,1:18:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,where the knowingness came to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.90,1:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.90,1:18:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you're beyond personal karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.90,1:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,now that you know
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.90,1:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no accountability for your actions,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.90,1:18:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,all power is yours only.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.31,1:18:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All power over the world is yours only.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.92,1:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.14,1:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the joke of it at the time was
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.14,1:18:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was experiencing the infinite power within
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.14,1:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.14,1:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,no, who the hell would want power?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.14,1:18:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What a drag.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.14,1:18:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You give your power over all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.14,1:18:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What a burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.14,1:19:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see what a horrible thing it would be?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.14,1:19:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which is complete and total
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.14,1:19:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,has no needs,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.14,1:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,including power, prestige, trappings, titles,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.14,1:19:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,power, prestige, trappings, titles.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.07,1:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need theatrics, robes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.00,1:19:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need to be Master Boom-gum-pum,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.16,1:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Boom-gum-pum, Mr. Boom-gum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.16,1:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Master Boom-gum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.16,1:19:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You come to ask me whether you can marry.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.75,1:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a teacher be interested
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.75,1:19:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you marry or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.75,1:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.94,1:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have defined
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.94,1:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the characteristics of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.13,1:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity in general.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.20,1:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll go back later.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.20,1:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a break
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.20,1:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll go back later
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.20,1:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to review a list of 144.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.55,1:19:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I've got another list of about 20.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.41,1:20:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,People are always sending me emails.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.17,1:20:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Master King Kong Boncho
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.17,1:20:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,who wrote a book about the end of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.17,1:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,coming in 32 years?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.17,1:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got 144 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.17,1:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And why does he have to drag this joker in?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.17,1:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.52,1:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll take a break
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.52,1:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with a sense of good humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.52,1:20:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.51,1:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Order in the court.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.70,1:20:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to consult my crib notes here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.70,1:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I bring the crib notes,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.50,1:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,things that I want to mention
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.50,1:20:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I forget the crib notes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.50,1:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.56,1:20:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, remember the bagpipes last time?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.95,1:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to be at St. Andrew's Episcopal Church
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.95,1:20:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sunday after Thanksgiving, November 27th.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.95,1:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be at St. Andrew's in Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.49,1:21:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Andrew's at the west end of town,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.49,1:21:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,100 Arroyo Pinyon Drive, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.49,1:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And church, I think, is at 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.49,1:21:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.49,1:21:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what time church starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.49,1:21:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, around there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.72,1:21:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing of interest
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.72,1:21:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because I like things that, you know, music
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.72,1:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrates above 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.72,1:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrea Bocelli is going to be on December 7th.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.72,1:21:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,December 8th.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.72,1:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Channel 8 at 8.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.72,1:21:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For those of you in Sedona or Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.84,1:21:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And 12-8 at 8 on 8.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.94,1:21:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrea Bocelli.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.94,1:21:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And he calibrates around, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.94,1:21:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think in the book 535 or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.94,1:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, kind of makes you weep with the beauty of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.12,1:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, 535 and up makes you weep.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.12,1:21:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So many people wept with the bagpipes
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.12,1:22:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and Bocelli makes you weep.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.32,1:22:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And great things.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.41,1:22:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Great stature and great meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.34,1:22:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the end of my list.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.34,1:22:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just those two things.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.63,1:22:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.63,1:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only handle two things,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.04,1:22:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so I only put two things on there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.49,1:22:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,12-8 on Channel 8 at 8.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.49,1:22:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty neat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.49,1:22:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.78,1:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.88,1:22:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.84,1:22:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Betty, what were we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.84,1:22:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There we were.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.00,1:22:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.00,1:22:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.00,1:22:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We ended up last time, the generalities,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.00,1:22:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about 35 different things that differentiate spiritual integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.00,1:22:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll go to a list,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.00,1:22:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which we also have in the form of a slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.00,1:22:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, someday we're going to publish a thing of all the slides.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.00,1:22:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All the slides.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.00,1:23:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a page of explanation in between each slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.00,1:23:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because somehow that gives it to you in an experiential, spatial way.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.00,1:23:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And your mind sort of gets what the essence is out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.00,1:23:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think the charts are useful, therefore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.00,1:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We went over this last time,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.79,1:23:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm not going to spend any time on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.79,1:23:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the general characteristics of spiritual integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.79,1:23:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that differentiates integral spiritual groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.79,1:23:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get so many questions about spiritual groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.79,1:23:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm repeating it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.85,1:23:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We get a lot of emails.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.85,1:23:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this teacher?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.85,1:23:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this method?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.85,1:23:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.95,1:23:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want people to have within themselves,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.95,1:23:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to differentiate on their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.04,1:23:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they out for gain?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.04,1:23:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they proselytizing?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.04,1:23:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they trying to sign you up?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.30,1:23:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a subtle form of brainwashing?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.30,1:23:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Some call them training sessions.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.13,1:23:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to be trained by anybody but you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.26,1:24:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, a training session.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.80,1:24:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of many of these things is,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.80,1:24:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in many workshops,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.80,1:24:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for which a great deal of money is charged,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.80,1:24:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,can be boiled down to maybe two sentences.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.80,1:24:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Many a workshop is built on maybe two sentences or two concepts.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.08,1:24:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that's elaborated.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.08,1:24:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How to use this to get more money.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.11,1:24:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there'll be a workshop on how to become richer using this technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.11,1:24:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then how to win the person that you want to win.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.11,1:24:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all the same tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.11,1:24:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.11,1:24:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell it to you for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.11,1:24:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.46,1:24:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.88,1:24:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiveness is the most rapid tool
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.16,1:24:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for rapid spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.96,1:24:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And all you have to do is ask yourself all the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.96,1:25:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,would you be willing to forgive and accept that which it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.96,1:25:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,considering Socrates' observation.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.96,1:25:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.96,1:25:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you do this over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.96,1:25:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So for $450, you can join me at some place.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.96,1:25:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.09,1:25:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus the room rate.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.80,1:25:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.89,1:25:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll just do it over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.89,1:25:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll get groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.40,1:25:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The six or eight of us will have individual groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.40,1:25:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And each one of us will practice it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.40,1:25:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, all they're doing is getting you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.40,1:25:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.24,1:25:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing is only about doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.24,1:25:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard it, but do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.72,1:25:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for $450, by God, you do it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.75,1:25:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.96,1:25:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it all day, then you do it in color blue,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.82,1:25:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then you do it in color green,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.96,1:25:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can take any workshop and give it to you in two sentences.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.73,1:25:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Two sentences.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.33,1:26:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering the basic innocence of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.11,1:26:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,would you be willing to forgive this person or this incident
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.21,1:26:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or this company or the price of oil?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.94,1:26:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course the company wants to make more money.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.44,1:26:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Exxon is a benevolent organization?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.06,1:26:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they're going to take advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.30,1:26:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're supposed to, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.06,1:26:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they supposed to make money?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.20,1:26:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Business is called making money.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.54,1:26:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to become a benevolent humanitarian organization,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.20,1:26:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a whole different script, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.58,1:26:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm president of a huge company and I start giving away money,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.68,1:26:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how long will I remain as president of the company?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.84,1:27:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So the bottom line of the ego is that it's lacking.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.57,1:27:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It must always get approval, get power over others, get glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.96,1:27:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the media today is the world of glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.26,1:27:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan was watching one the other day,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.04,1:27:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the both of us were just remarking on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.76,1:27:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, I've got the name and I just can't think of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.46,1:27:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, reality TV, reality TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.18,1:27:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality TV is the most...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.14,1:27:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,superficial, superfluous, unreal thing you've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.82,1:27:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In which artificial people are put in artificial circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.66,1:27:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,artificially decorated, artificially...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.64,1:27:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing is 100% artificiality.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.94,1:27:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called reality TV with a small r, a small r.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.60,1:27:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's entertaining, and there's nothing wrong with being entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.49,1:27:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So could you forgive yourself for being entertained by reality TV?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.91,1:28:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you forgive yourself for liking the vulgar?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.00,1:28:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you still love yourself even though you love that which is superficial and stupid?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.44,1:28:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you forgive yourself for chasing illusions?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.13,1:28:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you forgive yourself for not knowing anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.73,1:28:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you forgive yourself for rebirthing yourself every second?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.33,1:28:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You rebirth yourself every split second.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.96,1:28:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not every second.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.72,1:28:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's every one ten thousandths of a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.12,1:28:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When we track the perceiver, the perceiving edge,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.81,1:28:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencer edge of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.03,1:28:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which the amoeba needed in order to survive,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.27,1:29:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the cutting edge of the experiencer,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.01,1:29:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the front, it's like the prow of the ship
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.75,1:29:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that's cutting through the waves of experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.82,1:29:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting go of being dominated by that,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.84,1:29:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer identifying it as the self,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.04,1:29:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the self stops rebirthing itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.50,1:29:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The presumption is,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.60,1:29:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the presumption of the innocent mind
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.64,1:29:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it's at the effect of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.70,1:29:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at the effect of a linear causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.70,1:29:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So today I'm telling you,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.86,1:29:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not at the effect of a linear causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.86,1:29:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, by virtue of the Heisenberg principle on tension,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.86,1:29:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you can decide not to rebirth yourself every second.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.99,1:29:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose to let the finality be a finality, be a finality.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.61,1:29:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.61,1:29:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is supported by,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.68,1:29:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of being in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.68,1:29:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a contemplative way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.68,1:30:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplative, when you're contemplative,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.04,1:30:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't mean to do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.04,1:30:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the woods and it just is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.04,1:30:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So it moves you from acceptance to acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.07,1:30:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you begin to see
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.07,1:30:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that everything is emerging spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.07,1:30:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as the actualization of its potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.07,1:30:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is being caused by anything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.42,1:30:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.91,1:30:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution, then, is the unfolding of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.91,1:30:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution and creation are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.91,1:30:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so simple to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.00,1:30:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you think about it, it's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.00,1:30:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.45,1:30:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God created the world completely there and said,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.45,1:30:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.64,1:30:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That comes back at the end of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.64,1:30:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how ridiculous that is?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.74,1:31:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence is continuously present beyond all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.01,1:31:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is the birthing place
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.43,1:31:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in which potentiality becomes actuality.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.43,1:31:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The invocation, then, of intention
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.49,1:31:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,means that this potentiality will take precedence over this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.81,1:31:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have had pie or you could have had cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.81,1:31:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.34,1:31:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that all things are spontaneously emerging
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.72,1:31:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of that which they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.84,1:31:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What does a thing mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.84,1:31:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It means what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.26,1:31:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning and identity are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.26,1:31:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how dualistic it would be to say,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.26,1:31:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.26,1:31:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already split.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.26,1:31:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't mean this, that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.48,1:31:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This means this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.80,1:31:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.80,1:31:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Its meaning is its reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.80,1:32:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And its reality and its identity are one.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.80,1:32:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes you beyond duality and beyond linearity.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.19,1:32:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond linearity.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.19,1:32:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you accept your own reality in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.25,1:32:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.32,1:32:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not necessary to rebirth yourself every 10,000 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.32,1:32:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not bound to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.96,1:32:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.57,1:32:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.89,1:32:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.33,1:32:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there'll be a fee for telling you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.33,1:32:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have a workshop starting next week for $450
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.40,1:32:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Wuhan Resort
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.40,1:32:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in which Baba Bumpum
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.54,1:32:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,will take you through these two simple thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.28,1:32:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point of repetitious boredom.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.24,1:33:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because truth is not something you can grab for.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.12,1:33:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something you open yourself to.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.12,1:33:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've said that enlightenment is very, very yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.12,1:33:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is very, very yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.64,1:33:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is very, very yang.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.02,1:33:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.02,1:33:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It drives.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.02,1:33:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It craves.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.02,1:33:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It grasps.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.02,1:33:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It sobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.02,1:33:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It rips its face.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.02,1:33:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.82,1:33:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So yang is very pow.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.82,1:33:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And yin is very so.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.07,1:33:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The contemplative lifestyle, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.28,1:33:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you make your life a prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.35,1:33:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,your prayer is,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.67,1:33:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord God, reveal to me the truth of that which I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.67,1:33:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And by your stance, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.92,1:33:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you can even picture your spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.74,1:33:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in the form of a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.48,1:34:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the form of a mudra,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.48,1:34:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you walk through
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.92,1:34:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the phenomenal world
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.63,1:34:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as a question mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.16,1:34:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, something was out.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.35,1:34:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, dear God,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.76,1:34:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something out in this particular energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.76,1:34:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in this particular person.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.76,1:34:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.76,1:34:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.76,1:34:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness arose.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.92,1:34:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the arose,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.92,1:34:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness arises out of
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.92,1:34:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not knowingness, ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.92,1:34:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really arise
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.66,1:34:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,as a linear logical sequence of thought
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.66,1:34:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because I wouldn't have had to ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.92,1:34:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have figured it out myself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.92,1:34:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.11,1:34:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.11,1:34:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll go back to this
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.11,1:34:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll go on to individuals.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.17,1:34:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Much of spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.14,1:34:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,much of what goes on in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.14,1:34:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,called spiritual is slick.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.14,1:34:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very slick.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.27,1:35:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like reality TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.27,1:35:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.27,1:35:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality, spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.27,1:35:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Very big.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.64,1:35:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful diaphanous girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.64,1:35:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very slick magazine.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.64,1:35:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Very slick.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.09,1:35:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of the people
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.05,1:35:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,who write for these,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.05,1:35:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,including myself,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.08,1:35:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,are writing about spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.82,1:35:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,About.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.82,1:35:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not talking from the experiential.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.82,1:35:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're talking from the descriptive.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.82,1:35:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Descriptive.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.30,1:35:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you understand that,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.30,1:35:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,there's that which has learned things
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.30,1:35:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,through inner experience
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.30,1:35:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and it comes about as a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.30,1:35:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't come as a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.30,1:35:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't come about as logic.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.30,1:35:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't come about as a consequence of study.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.56,1:35:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the only thing study can do
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.56,1:35:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is expose you to a truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.56,1:35:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But then it's your application within yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.56,1:35:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the payoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.56,1:35:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not reading the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.59,1:35:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very ignorant of religious history
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.59,1:36:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the details of many religions.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.88,1:36:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've tried to get more acquainted with it,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.13,1:36:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's too staggeringly detailed
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.34,1:36:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.27,1:36:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you know that E equals MC squared,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.28,1:36:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes about.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.28,1:36:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's preparatory work, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.02,1:36:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You go through the linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.02,1:36:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's preparatory.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.02,1:36:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But then,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.18,1:36:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,how it is that E equals MC squared
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.85,1:36:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,comes out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.85,1:36:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you're eating a cheese sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.85,1:36:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,God, how simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.85,1:36:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.85,1:36:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.33,1:36:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that which is true
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.33,1:36:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is universally true throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.56,1:36:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we'll have to forget about
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.56,1:36:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the world being in 23 years
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.56,1:36:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or 52 years or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.56,1:36:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which is universally true
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.56,1:36:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is non-linear, beyond all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.59,1:37:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it is not,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.59,1:37:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it cannot be predicted.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.94,1:37:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Prediction is within the linear causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.10,1:37:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a prediction that an angry god
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.10,1:37:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in the year 3042
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.10,1:37:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to destroy mankind and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.10,1:37:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the prophecies of the end of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.10,1:37:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,have been with us
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.10,1:37:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,since even before the Old Testament.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.55,1:37:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of the worlders.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.55,1:37:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There used to be a journal called
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.55,1:37:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,End Times Review or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.55,1:37:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was back in the 70s or 80s.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.55,1:37:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was popular.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.55,1:37:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody was into the end of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.55,1:37:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,back in the 70s or 80s.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.55,1:37:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And that sort of lost its popularity.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.90,1:37:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And they changed the dates,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.90,1:37:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but that didn't help any.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.90,1:37:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we got new ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.90,1:37:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get panicky emails, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.90,1:37:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this book?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.90,1:37:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prophecies of the World
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.90,1:37:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to end in the year 6082.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.90,1:37:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, don't let it worry you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.96,1:37:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to be around anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.96,1:38:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.96,1:38:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.96,1:38:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's available to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.19,1:38:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity of purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.19,1:38:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to gain or lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.19,1:38:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You merely want to share what you've discovered.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.19,1:38:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So the position from which I teach
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.51,1:38:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is very much the same as Fleming.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.51,1:38:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He discovered what penicillin could do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.51,1:38:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.64,1:38:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he saw the implication.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.64,1:38:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't sleep with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.83,1:38:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.83,1:38:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ran around for five years.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.12,1:38:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was a different paradigm of reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.12,1:38:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he got nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.12,1:38:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And only because of World War II,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.82,1:38:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the infections killing off the soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.82,1:38:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,did the United States Army pay attention to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.82,1:38:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, he couldn't rest with his music,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.33,1:38:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,without having played his music,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.33,1:38:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,without his song having been unsung.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.33,1:38:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he saw the value to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.33,1:38:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was his motivation.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.33,1:38:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To share what he had learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.33,1:39:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For its intrinsic value to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.33,1:39:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the motivation, if there is such a thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.33,1:39:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.33,1:39:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teacher is available.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.33,1:39:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity of purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.33,1:39:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't own the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.33,1:39:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Devoid of positionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.33,1:39:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is not anti-anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.33,1:39:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite of truth, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.75,1:39:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is the opposite of truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.75,1:39:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite of truth is the absence of truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.84,1:39:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the book, Truth vs. Falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.84,1:39:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we try to make that clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.84,1:39:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's either truth or its absence.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.84,1:39:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.84,1:39:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a dualistic set of opposites.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.88,1:39:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Light is either present or not present.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.07,1:39:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's not present, we call it darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.07,1:39:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But darkness is not the opposite of light.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.07,1:39:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.07,1:39:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the absence.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.07,1:39:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Falsehood is the absence.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.68,1:39:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Devoid of positionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.68,1:39:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sign up for anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.68,1:39:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No oaths, no rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.68,1:39:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-controlling.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.68,1:39:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't want to control what you should wear or eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.68,1:39:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No force or intimidation.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.87,1:40:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.25,1:40:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.25,1:40:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-binding.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.25,1:40:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sign up for anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.41,1:40:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's free to come or go.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.41,1:40:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's free to either listen or not listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.53,1:40:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.53,1:40:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-materialistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.53,1:40:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.98,1:40:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The work should be,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.98,1:40:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried to make the work that I do,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.98,1:40:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so complete and total,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.98,1:40:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that's bulwarked.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.98,1:40:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bulwarked.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.98,1:40:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.98,1:40:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't believe in this or that,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.98,1:40:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the bulwark keeps it from being misinterpreted
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.98,1:40:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.98,1:40:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.35,1:40:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, move to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.96,1:40:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.96,1:40:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Means that it's non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.96,1:40:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.96,1:40:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute truth is beyond linearity.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.96,1:40:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Linearity is what?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.96,1:40:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Definition and time and place and specifics.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.96,1:40:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And truth is beyond all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.37,1:40:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is linear is confined
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.04,1:41:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to the consciousness level of the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.04,1:41:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the best a skeptic can do is say
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.36,1:41:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't believe in faith,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.36,1:41:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't believe in miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.36,1:41:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't believe in saints.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.36,1:41:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because within the linear domain,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.55,1:41:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that is not their experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.55,1:41:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're being honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.77,1:41:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of what in the book we call lower mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.77,1:41:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The lower mind is very pedestrian,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.77,1:41:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,literal, concrete.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.77,1:41:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get the abstract.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.77,1:41:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get significance.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.77,1:41:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.77,1:41:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because those are non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.77,1:41:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like love is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.77,1:41:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you prove that love exists?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.77,1:41:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.77,1:41:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If something brings you delight,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.77,1:41:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,can you prove delight?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.77,1:41:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.77,1:41:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So although the skeptic sensibly lives in that,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.77,1:41:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he does it because he gets enjoyment out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.77,1:41:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he get enjoyment?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.77,1:41:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.77,1:41:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the payoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.77,1:41:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He denies the existence of the very purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.77,1:41:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for which he's writing the book in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.77,1:41:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's beyond all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.77,1:41:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tranquil, non-temporality, beyond proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.12,1:42:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is provable is not the highest spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.16,1:42:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is confirmable, we confirm it,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.16,1:42:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but we don't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.16,1:42:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mystical in that the source originates from within.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.16,1:42:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Religiosity is a matter of study of that which is without,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.35,1:42:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the attempt to make it also within.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.35,1:42:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ineffable, not capable of definition.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.35,1:42:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The states that I describe experientially,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.76,1:42:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,which began in early childhood
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.76,1:42:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and recurred throughout life,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.08,1:42:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,are ineffable.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.08,1:42:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't really be described in ordinary,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.08,1:42:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's outside of ordinary human experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.08,1:42:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's called mystical.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.98,1:42:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Simplistic, affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.43,1:42:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth does not do anything or cause anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.59,1:42:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth attracts.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.59,1:42:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to attract rather than proselytize.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.68,1:42:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.68,1:43:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotionality is of a different domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.68,1:43:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotionality is an outpouring of animal emotionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.09,1:43:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-authoritarian.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.09,1:43:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no rules or dictates.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.51,1:43:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it stems from certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.80,1:43:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainty is different than authoritarian.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.56,1:43:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It stems from an inner certainty of knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.56,1:43:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes beyond logic or reason,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.56,1:43:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,just as the awareness,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.32,1:43:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which came forth periodically in life,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.18,1:43:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,just as the awareness that the self is reborn every instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.66,1:43:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to Susie,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.66,1:43:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, wow, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.48,1:43:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.48,1:43:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.92,1:43:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See, if you thought that up,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.37,1:44:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't do that about it, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.37,1:44:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because it would be vanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.60,1:44:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when it comes from without,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.60,1:44:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be ecstatic about it because it's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.60,1:44:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It just comes out of a yin positionality, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.72,1:44:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The being open to the revelation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.72,1:44:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-authoritarian, but certain.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.40,1:44:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, freestanding on its own,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.40,1:44:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,self-supporting and natural,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.23,1:44:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,devoid of altered states of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.23,1:44:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am not an enthusiast
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.23,1:44:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for manipulating kundalini energy
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.23,1:44:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,by
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.23,1:44:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing techniques,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.26,1:44:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,postures,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.26,1:44:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or any other grotesque distortions
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.26,1:44:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of normal human behavior.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.26,1:44:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because it's insurious.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.00,1:44:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.00,1:44:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when your consciousness level is at a certain point,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.32,1:44:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the kundalini energy flows to that which you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.32,1:44:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.32,1:44:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It automatically summons it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.32,1:45:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you try to force it ahead of time,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.32,1:45:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then you end up
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.32,1:45:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with difficulties,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.32,1:45:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,religious psychosis,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.32,1:45:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and various things.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.32,1:45:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember a guy sitting on the floor telling me,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.32,1:45:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's Jesus Christ, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.32,1:45:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he just overdid it, is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.75,1:45:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He did, yeah, he overdid it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.09,1:45:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-predictive, non-sentimental,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.09,1:45:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,non-authoritarian, non-egoistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.09,1:45:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freestanding,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.22,1:45:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not artificially induced.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.22,1:45:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean that health,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.22,1:45:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,things that support health, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.22,1:45:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a healthy body and a healthy mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.22,1:45:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the Latin phrase.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.22,1:45:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the Latin phrase?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.80,1:45:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Incendio, incendio, Santa.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.80,1:45:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.80,1:45:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Healthy mind and healthy body, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.80,1:45:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the experience of the joy of life,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.99,1:45:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you then enjoy the physicality of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.99,1:46:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.08,1:46:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the end of it, 38?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.08,1:46:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.72,1:46:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, there's 144 of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.76,1:46:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,144, plus I jotted down another 20 or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.72,1:46:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no shortage of spiritual truth out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.42,1:46:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These have all been calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.71,1:46:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all, I guess they meet all the criteria.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.71,1:46:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They meet all the criteria,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.71,1:46:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best of our understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.71,1:46:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've drawn them from a number of different
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.84,1:46:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,religious backgrounds, spiritual backgrounds,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.25,1:46:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,different eras.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.25,1:46:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The first enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.41,1:46:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,really enlightened sages,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.41,1:46:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,emerged in the Aryan pre-India
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.41,1:46:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of about 5000 BC.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.41,1:46:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,About 5000 BC,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.99,1:46:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the great sages began to appear
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.99,1:46:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in ancient India.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.99,1:47:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so here's 144.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.93,1:47:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They all calibrate extremely well.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.93,1:47:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all withstood the test of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.93,1:47:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll go back,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.93,1:47:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,starting with the previous list,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.93,1:47:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we've got some more, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.32,1:47:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of catalogs that popularize spiritual books,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.83,1:47:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,they tend to be a little overly slick to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.83,1:47:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of them are over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.83,1:47:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We recently, we got one yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.08,1:47:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the day before.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.08,1:47:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the catalog, thank God,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.08,1:47:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,was over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.08,1:47:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of them were the 200s, 300s,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.08,1:47:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,occasionally 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.08,1:47:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And one or two at 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.50,1:47:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are descriptions of spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.82,1:47:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you start with,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.85,1:47:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,start with spiritual learning?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.85,1:47:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You start by inspiration,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.85,1:48:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get attracted to reading certain books.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.85,1:48:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And you begin to accumulate spiritual knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.85,1:48:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,which will later become experiential.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.85,1:48:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of these levels is not better than another.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.46,1:48:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first illusion we want to remove
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.46,1:48:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is that a higher number means better than.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.52,1:48:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A higher number doesn't mean better than.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.77,1:48:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who calibrates at 700
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.77,1:48:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,makes no sense at all to the audience,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.77,1:48:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all walk away,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.77,1:48:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and what the hell was that about?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.93,1:48:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody at 250 who can give you a practical technique
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.93,1:48:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that changes your life
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.03,1:48:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is far more valuable.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.03,1:48:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So each level then
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.03,1:48:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,describes the truth of that level.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.03,1:48:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth of this level here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.06,1:48:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the truth of this level here
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.06,1:48:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the same as the truth of this level here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.51,1:48:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.51,1:48:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So each level then
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.73,1:48:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,denotes a level of conscious awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.96,1:49:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not better than.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.00,1:49:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody with a consciousness level of 210
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.03,1:49:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,who starts reading the Dhammapada
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.03,1:49:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't going to make any sense out of it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.03,1:49:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.44,1:49:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's intellectually interesting,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.44,1:49:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but not really useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.57,1:49:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.57,1:49:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,start with humility
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.57,1:49:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and say,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.57,1:49:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I should do
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.57,1:49:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is go back to the basics
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.57,1:49:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and see have I got that.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.57,1:49:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I got the willingness
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.50,1:49:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to forgive everything and everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.50,1:49:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.24,1:49:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.12,1:49:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I got step number one
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.41,1:49:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,before I'm reaching for step number 32.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.53,1:49:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to forgive yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.53,1:49:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.92,1:49:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive everything
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.92,1:50:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that you hear and see on the media
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.92,1:50:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and see it all as a panorama.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.92,1:50:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all projection and perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.92,1:50:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The projections of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.92,1:50:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.17,1:50:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we have such spiritual advantages
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.17,1:50:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's world.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.64,1:50:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In times past you could spend your whole life
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.64,1:50:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,just being a sheep herder
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.64,1:50:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in a small little community
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.64,1:50:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and not know more than a few dozen people.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.64,1:50:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can sit in front of your television set.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.99,1:50:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire panorama of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.99,1:50:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is projected for your view.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.34,1:50:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can experience more
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.34,1:50:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and have more life decisions
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.34,1:50:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in a couple of minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.52,1:50:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,than you could in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.52,1:50:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How many options do you have
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.52,1:50:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,as a sheep herder in a small village
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.52,1:50:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.75,1:50:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Very few options.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.23,1:50:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you can turn on
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.23,1:50:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and there you've got a million options,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.23,1:50:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,perceptions, projections
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.23,1:51:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of value, of goodness, of badness,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.23,1:51:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of evil, of desirability.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.23,1:51:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ego has a major workshop now
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.23,1:51:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for free.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.23,1:51:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.80,1:51:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A great gift because it speeds up time.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.80,1:51:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make a thousand decisions,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.80,1:51:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a thousand observations
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.80,1:51:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and it would have taken you a thousand lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.80,1:51:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the first thing to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.54,1:51:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that each level is
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.54,1:51:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,describing a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.76,1:51:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like depths below the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.76,1:51:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain fish live at certain depths
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.76,1:51:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and a different kind of fish live here
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.76,1:51:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and a different kind of fish here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.76,1:51:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the grouper lives down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.76,1:51:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The grouper doesn't live up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.76,1:51:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're looking on this level
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.89,1:51:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for grouperism, you won't find any
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.89,1:51:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,because they don't group up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.99,1:51:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A grouper is a big, monstrous fish
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.99,1:51:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and he eats whole lobsters.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.99,1:51:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you doing all those good lobsters,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.99,1:51:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,eating up the good lobsters.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.99,1:51:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,One grouper will eat up a thousand dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.99,1:52:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,worth of lobsters in a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.99,1:52:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We need fewer groupers
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.95,1:52:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and more lobsters, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.95,1:52:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how you project the value.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.36,1:52:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well, a lobster is worth more
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.36,1:52:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,than a grouper.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.36,1:52:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not so.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.05,1:52:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lobsterism.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.05,1:52:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Grouperism.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.60,1:52:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can go to battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.56,1:52:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the lobsters?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.26,1:52:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And those are the groupers.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.26,1:52:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will kill each other
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.26,1:52:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because grouper people are evil
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.26,1:52:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and lobster people are good
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.26,1:52:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or vice versa.
